name: Foss-on
body:
# FOSS-On! \m/

This project (apart from earning us 10 marks. :P) is also going to be a birthday gift for one of our closest friends.
We won't be revealing much here since we don't want the surprise to be spoilt

She's quite a public figure with a facebook fan page of her own so I'm sure all you fangirls and fanboys out there will be equally excited about this project as much as we are.

Unfortunately, you will have to wait till April 20th to know what it is, but I promise you it's worth the wait. :D

Keep visiting our site, we might throw a couple of hints on what this is about. ;)
